description:
In a stunning and silent change of events...the CDC has now updated their website to reflect that only 6% of the total Covid-19 deaths have specifically come from China Virus alone. The other 94% of deaths have 2-3 serious underlying health issues that could have contributed to death.
That would make the total number of deaths resulting from just China Virus alone to be 9,210. ITS TIME TO TAKE OFF THE MASKS! www.CDC.gov
